to a local database.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage","abstract":[{"text":"MLNOfflineStorage implements a singleton (shared object) that manages offline","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its ","type":"text"},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNOfflineStorage","role":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflineStorage"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackprogresschangednotification","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","title":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Posted by the shared "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage"},{"type":"text","text":" object when an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object’s progress changes. The progress may change due to a resource being"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"downloaded or because the pack discovers during the download that more"},{"type":